Politicians like Trump wearing fake hair and spray tanning himself in excess to be better liked for example.

Think to yourself back to a time when you were a child. You dressed how you wanted without a care in the world. Your hair could be messy, you could have spinach in your teeth, dirt under your nails, and you didn't give one single fuck about how you looked just what adventure you were going on. Now that you're older, every time you turn on the tv, your phone, or drive down the road you're seeing stuff plastered and shoved into your face about change this about you or you look a certain way to fit in.
